Passage 48
季节性 因为要 海藻 季节性的
证明了没有其他吃的

选E


理解大概的意思  当时粗体字的细节并没有很明白  
答案很清楚


分析单词 和加粗句子

drift 漂流 反应速度不够
raining down 沉降 速度不够

So far, researchers have found no evidence of seasonal breeding among vent-dwelling species that provide their offspring with yolk to sustain them or among vent-dwelling species found in areas of the ocean with not seasonal algae blooms.
分析句子结构  
dwelling 居住!!!!! 很重要  没看懂  影响理解 
vent-dwelling 居住在火山口附近的 物种
no evidence of seasonal breeding among vent-dwelling speciesa
没有 在所有火山口居住的物种的中  季节性 繁殖的 证据
among vent-dwelling speciesa 
在所有 物种中!!!!!!!!

yolk 蛋黄! 这里指代幼虫要的营养物质

or among vent-dwelling species found in areas of the ocean with not seasonal algae blooms
也没有在所有火山口物种中找到 季节藻类突增的



So far, researchers have found no evidence of seasonal breeding among vent-dwelling species that provide their offspring with yolk to sustain them or among vent-dwelling species found in areas of the ocean with not seasonal algae blooms.